== ubuzima ==
Tamara Hoekwatere yize mu ishuri rya Muzika [[Maastricht]]. Kuva mu 1992 kugeza 2002 yari umuririmbyi wambere witsinda rya pop [[Volumia!]]<Ref>[http://www.dichtbij.nl/t-gooi/regionaal-nieuws/artikel/3527225/doek-valt-al-voor-de-pianobar.aspx ]</ref>

Nyuma ya Volumia! yaririmbye mu itsinda rinini '' Igishushanyo mbonera ''. Kuva mu 2002 yagaragaye muri "The Jack Million Big-Band," ikaba yaravuzweho byinshi mu miyoborere n’ububanyi n’amahanga muri Amerika. Muri rumwe muri izo ngendo bitabiriye [[Glenn Miller | Glenn-Miller]] - Ibirori muri [[Clarinda]], [[Iowa]]. Mu [[Umujyi wa New York]] yakinnye na Greg Walker ([Santana (itsinda) | Santana]]). Kuri televiziyo [[Limburg 1 | L1]] yerekana urukundo rwe rwerekana nka "Agaciro Kumwanya" na "Tamara & Birgit".

Niba ufite ikibazo kijyanye numuntu [[Björn Stenvers]] muri [[Amsterdam]], nyamuneka hamagara Jazzkarriere hamwe na [[Cees Hamelink]] na "Bourgondisch Combo" (itsinda ryinzu ya [[Kaminuza ya Amsterdam]])) Imikorere muri - kandi ikorera hanze. <ref>[https://bourgondischcombo.wordpress.com/about/ Bourgondisch Combo]</ref><ref>[https://aac.uva.nl/content/evenementen/evenementen/2018/10/amsterdams-jazz-cafe---5-Oktubre---bourgondisch-combo.html ]</ref>Niadtong 3 Oktubre 2014 ilang gipagawas ang ilang CD '' Ik zei ja '' sa Amsterdams Jazz Amsterdamse Academische Club Café. Ku ya 3 Ukwakira 2014, CD ya "Ik zei ja" izasohoka muri Amsterdam Jazz Café ya Amsterdamse Academische Club. <ref>[https://www.jazzhelden.nl jazzhelden.nl]</ref> Kuva mu 2015 yazengurutse inshuro nyinshi hamwe na 'Quartet ya Maynugin' muri [[Uburusiya]]. Akora kandi muri babiri hamwe numucuranga w inzogera na Frank Steijns ucuranga inanga hamwe na quartet ye.<ref>[https://www.amstelveenweb.com/nieuws-Het-Tamara-Hoekwater-Quartet-treedt-op-in-Elsrij&newsid=346494771]</ref> Kanama 2016 ntikiraboneka kuri [[Museum Het Rembrandthuis]] i Amsterdam hamwe n’icyayi n’ikawa idasanzwe.<Ref>[https://www.amsterdamsdagblad.nl/proef-nu-de-koffie-van-de-maand-bij-simon-levelt-jodenbreestraat ]</ref><ref>[https://www.amsterdamsdagblad.nl/proef-nu-de-koffie-van-de-texts-bij-simon-levelt-jodenbreestraat amsterdamsdagblad.nl]</ref><ref>[https://www.simonlevelt.nl/winkels/amsterdam-jodenbreestraat ]</ref>

